Large-Cap Income — New Vernon Wealth Management










































New Vernon Wealth Management




















Large-Cap IncomeThis particular strategy seeks dividend income through well-know, multi-national companies with a long history of increasing their dividend annually.These companies have revenue from around the globe and are clear market leaders in their industries.  They have superb balance sheets, and have shown an ability to navigate through virtually any economic cycles & conditions.Our View: We believe this is an attractive alternative to traditional, high-quality corporate fixed income; in fact, for many of these stocks, their dividend yields exceed their 10 year bond yields.Contact us for more information.




 











