About Thomas H. Patrick of  NEW VERNON CAPITAL



									
										   Thomas H. Patrick is Chairman at New Vernon Capital Holdings Ii Llc and has been affiliated with New Vernon Capital Holdings Ii Llc since November-2004. New Vernon Capital Holdings Ii Llc is an investment advisor that manages 908.9 MM dollars in regulatory AUM and has 18 employees, of which 7 perform investment advisory functions. The managers's latest filing has disclosed 54MM in positions, which represents 6% of the manager's regulatory AUM.  For more on New Vernon Capital Holdings Ii Llc including top positions, information on the investment process, service provider information, other key employees, real time performance, 13-F holdings and more visit the Fund Profile







